  h2.docs-section Colors

  h3 The Codebase swatch

  p.
    The default Codebase swatch re-purposes the control colors (<span class="label label--primary">primary</span>, <span class="label label--secondary">secondary</span>, <span class="label label--warning">warning</span>, <span class="label label--error">error</span>, <span class="label label--success">success</span>) as decoration colors (<span class="text-blue">blue</span>, <span class="text-blue">teal</span>, <span class="text-orange">orange</span>, <span class="text-red">red</span>, <span class="text-green">green</span> respectively), and adds black, gray and white. A series of lighter and darker variants of each color have been generated (except for black and white).

  p You can override and add to these colors in your own theme.
